name: Chesha Thompson
review: Great reformed theology church with welcoming congregation. If you’re looking for biblical expository preaching of the Word, come here! All ages and families here.

name: Elliott Harvey
review: Spent 17 years growing up here. Sometimes good, but if you have a DV situation that you’re trying to get out of don’t come here.

review: A great reformed Church with members of all ages
